_sText:
Bomb-Defuse

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists
from bombing artifact crates.
Team members must defuse any bombs 
that threaten targeted areas.

Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the
C4 must destroy one of the old 
artifact stashes. 

Spawn points: 32
Bots Support: No  
Environment : Village, Valley, Town

Author: Xzertel
